OL,3,CMan dies after 'violent and shocking
OL,4,Cattack'
OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway
OL,7,Fafter a man's "violent and shocking"
OL,8,Fdeath.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police responded to
OL,11,Freports of an assault at a business
OL,12,Fproperty on Bow Street, Ashton Under-
OL,13,FLyne at around 2:40am on Saturday 11
OL,14,FJuly 2026.
OL,16,FA man in his early 30s was found with
OL,17,Fserious injuries but despite best
OL,18,Fefforts of emergency services, he was
OL,19,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
