OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783871341
OL,3,CMan dies after 'violent and shocking
OL,4,Cattack'
OL,6,FOne man, aged 36, has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder and remains in
OL,8,Fcustody for questioning.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent Ian McNabb
OL,11,Fsaid: "This is was a violent and
OL,12,Fshocking attack that tragically took
OL,13,Fthe life of a young man. Our thoughts
OL,14,Fremain with his family and loved ones
OL,15,Fat this difficult time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783871341
OL,3,CMan dies after 'violent and shocking
OL,4,Cattack'
OL,6,F"We are working at pace to establish
OL,7,Fthe full circumstances of this
OL,8,Fincident, and whilst no formal
OL,9,Fidentification has taken place yet,
OL,10,Fthe believed family of the victim has
OL,11,Fbeen informed and is being supported
OL,12,Fby our specialist officers.
OL,14,F"We currently have a man in our
OL,15,Fcustody and a scene is still in place
OL,16,Fat this time. We would also like to
OL,17,Freassure the community we believe this
OL,18,Fto be an isolated attack and poses no
OL,19,Fwider threat to the public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
