PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1783871341
OL,3,CMan dies after 'violent and shocking
OL,4,Cattack'
OL,6,F"As we are still in the early stages
OL,7,Fof our investigation, we are appealing
OL,8,Ffor anyone who may have information to
OL,9,Fplease come forward and report.
OL,11,F"This can be anyone who may have
OL,12,Fwitnessed the incident itself, or has
OL,13,Fany footage from the area that may
OL,14,Fsupport our enquiries."
OL,16,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,17,Fcontact on 0161 856 1995.
OL,19,FAlternatively, you can contact the
OL,20,Findependent charity Crimestoppers,
OL,21,Fanonymously, on 0800 555 111.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
